 undefined">Make the world&#x27;s most sophisticated network science yours</h2><div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-10 max-reading-width"><div class="adaptive-text-s !text-text-secondary"><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 gap-md"><div class="flex flex-col gap-xs "><p class="">The Internet Computer was developed by a multi-year R&amp;D program. After initial work, the DFINITY Foundation was formed October 2016, and has run the largest R&amp;D operation in the Web3 industry since late 2017.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-xs "><p class="">Its purpose is to develop internet cloud that hosts a new kind of software (any language that compiles to Wasm can be used, but DFINITY also develops the domain-specific Motoko language). Over the years, the network&#x27;s development has benefited from the work of some of the world&#x27;s brightest researchers and engineers in areas such as secure distributed protocols, cryptography, execution environments, WASM and languages.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-xs "><p class="">In recent times, an increasing emphasis has been placed on enabling the self-writing internet, where AI generates apps on demand. As the Internet Computer hosts ever more apps and services, it becomes increasingly clear that its time has come.</p></div></div></div><div class="@container w-full max-w-3xl rounded-lg space-y-6 "><div class="flex flex-col @md:flex-row flex-wrap items-start @md:items-center gap-6"><a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#0979687b7d676c7b7a616079496d6f6067607d7027667b6e" class="group btn-base transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth px-4 py-2 text-s gap-2 w-fit rounded-md bg-white-12 text-text-primary hover:bg-white-18 active:bg-white-18 hover:text-text-primary active:text-text-primary "><span class="">Get in touch</span></a><a href="https://theconversation.com/europe-wants-to-end-its-dangerous-reliance-on-us-internet-technology-274042" class="group btn-base transition-all duration-200 ease-smooth py-2 gap-2 text-s text-text-